=== Sample Size Justification

Based on preliminary data:
    - Assumed control arm crash rate: 3 per month (36 over 6 months)
    - Clinically meaningful reduction: 40% (to 1.8 per month)
    - With n=30 per arm: 80% power at $alpha$=0.05
    - Accounts for 15% dropout


